><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1757943963689" class="gf_row gf_row-fluid gf_row-no-padding" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1757943963689" data-extraclass=""><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1757943963691" data-id="1757943963691"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709026996382" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709026996382" data-layout-lg="8+4" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="8+4" data-layout-sm="12+12" data-layout-xs="12+12" data-row-gap="0px"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-8 gf_col-md-8 gf_col-xs-12 gf_col-sm-12" id="c-1685509315590" data-id="1685509315590"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996356" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709026996356"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="" data-lt-tmp-id="lt-763099" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false"><h1 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Das perfekte Geschenk für Mechaniker u.- Motorliebhaber - magische Mechaniker-Tasse voller Liebe zum Detail</font></h1></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996419" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996419"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#878282">Konrad Kronenberg | Publiziert vor 2 Stunden</font></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1757944486718" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1757944486718"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p><strong>Mehr als nur eine Tasse – das ultimative Geschenk für Männer, die Motoren lieben</strong></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709562165566" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709562165566" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/ea0a7470-aa9d-492a-99d1-dfbdc27d2a5f/-/format/auto/-/preview/120x120/-/quality/lighter/09068fe3-54d7-4b82-86f1-c60eae9c373e.png" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1536" natural-height="1024" width="1536" height="1024" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709026996388" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709026996388"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><font color="#000000">Zum 50. Geburtstag hatte ich mir eigentlich nichts Besonderes erhofft.</font></p><p><font color="#000000"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;">Nur ein ruhiger Nachmittag in der Werkstatt, etwas Ölgeruch in der Luft und vielleicht ein paar Stunden, um an meinem alten Motorrad zu schrauben.</font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;">Doch als mein Sohn mir ein kleines, schweres Päckchen überreichte, lachte ich noch:</font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;">„Ach, das wäre doch nicht nötig gewesen – ich hab doch schon alles, was ich brauche.“</font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;">Aber dann öffnete ich das Papier. Und mir stockte der Atem.</font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;">Es war eine Tasse… aber nicht irgendeine Tasse.</font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;">So etwas hatte ich in all meinen Jahren noch nie gesehen.</font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000" style="font-weight: normal;">Auf den ersten Blick wirkte sie wie ein detailgetreuer Miniatur-Motorblock – voller Schrauben, Kolben, Zahnräder und feinster Handarbeit.</font></p><p><font color="#000000"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000">Doch beim genaueren Hinsehen wurde klar: Es war eine handgemachte Tasse, geformt wie ein Meisterstück der Ingenieurskunst.</font></p><p><font color="#000000"><br></font></p><p><font color="#000000">Fast so, als hätte jemand all meine Leidenschaft für Motoren und Maschinen in Keramik gegossen.</font></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p><p><font color="#000000"><span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></font></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1714045396277" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1714045396277" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0815/6889/1219/files/Gen-4Turbocanyouanimatethispouringthehotwaterin883328213-ezgif.com-gif-to-webp-converter_120x120.webp?v=1757671244" alt="" class="gf_image gf_lazyload" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="800" natural-height="450" width="800" height="450" loading="lazy" data-lg-size="3000x3000"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1713946259430" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gp